Package: rtimecapsule
Type: Package
Title: Automatic Backup for R Scripts, Rmd, and Quarto Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Yihun",
      family = "Zeleke",
      email = "yihunshegnew@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: 
    Provides automatic tracking and backup of R scripts (.R), R Markdown (.Rmd), and Quarto (.qmd) files
    within an RStudio project. The package creates timestamped backups in a hidden `.rtimecapsule` folder
    whenever a file changes, and allows restoring previous versions. Designed to be lightweight and dependency-free.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
